title: SARA'S FAMOUS CHERRY CRISP
directions: Place two cans of LUCKY LEAF Cherry Pie Filling in bottom of 9" x 13" pan.
Blend softened butter, oatmeal, brown sugar and pecans until it is crumbly.
Sprinkle all of mixture over top of the pie filling.
Bake for 30 minutes or until golden brown.
